Illuminate

Raises evasiveness.

Details

In Pokemon Voyager, this ability has a new in-battle effect: the wielder's evasiveness is raised as though they were holding a Bright Powder.

In the overworld, if your lead Pokemon has this ability then the wild encounter rate is doubled.
